# Language

This repo uses English as natural language.

## Code Generation

- All code comments, documentation, and strings should be written in English
- Variable names, function names, and class names should use English naming conventions
- Error messages and log messages should be in English

## Git Commits

- All commit messages must be written in English
- Use conventional commit format when appropriate (e.g., "feat:", "fix:", "docs:", etc.)

